    • Constructor Detail

      • DynObjectIteratorWCSInfo

        public DynObjectIteratorWCSInfo(Object info)
        Creates a new DynObjects iterator facade over a feature iterator. Each WMTSInfo will be returned through a new or reused DynObjectWMTSInfo which allows the Feature to be used like a DynObject.
        Parameters:
        featureIterator - to facade
        featureFacade - if not null this object will be reused as the facade for the Feature objects of the feature iterator
